			<div class="l-prose gh-content">
				<p>
					The Entrepreneurship and Innovation course is designed for aspiring entrepreneurs and business-minded individuals who want to turn ideas into reality. This course will guide you through the entrepreneurial journey—from identifying opportunities and validating ideas to building innovative solutions and managing growth. You’ll gain practical tools, case studies, and strategies that help you think creatively, solve real-world problems, and develop a sustainable business model. Whether you’re starting from scratch or looking to grow an existing venture, this course equips you with the mindset and skills to succeed in today’s competitive market.
				</p>
				<p><strong>What You’ll Learn:</strong></p>
				<ul>
					<li>Understanding the fundamentals of entrepreneurship</li>
					<li>Identifying business opportunities and market gaps</li>
					<li>Developing innovative ideas and solutions</li>
					<li>Building a business model and value proposition</li>
					<li>Basics of funding, pitching, and financial planning</li>
					<li>Strategies for scaling and sustaining a startup</li>
					<li>Cultivating an entrepreneurial mindset for long-term success</li>
				</ul>
